    • getContentDiv

      public Tag getContentDiv()
      Description copied from interface: Navs
      Navs outputs nav container and content div one after another which works fine for horizontal tabs/pills. However, for vertial pills it outputs the pills above the content. Use this method and toHTMLElement() to output navs and content divs independently, e.g. each into a col in a row.
      Specified by:
      getContentDiv in interface Navs
